{"auditid":"0","label":"","text":"<div id=\"Ps.98\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"ms2\">Salmo 98 (97)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Aclamen al Se\u00f1or, el rey<\/h3>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_1\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.1\" class=\"v19_98_1\">1<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Salmo<\/span>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_1\">Canten al Se\u00f1or un c\u00e1ntico nuevo<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_1\">porque ha hecho maravillas;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_1\">su diestra, su santo brazo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_1\">le ha dado la victoria.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_2\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.2\" class=\"v19_98_2\">2<\/sup>El Se\u00f1or ha proclamado su victoria,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_2\">ante las naciones desvela su justicia.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.3\" class=\"v19_98_3\">3<\/sup>Ha recordado su amor y su verdad<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_3\">hacia la casa de Israel,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_3\">han visto los confines de la tierra<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_3\">la victoria de nuestro Dios.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.4\" class=\"v19_98_4\">4<\/sup>Aclama al Se\u00f1or tierra entera,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_4\">griten de j\u00fabilo, al\u00e9grense, canten.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.5\" class=\"v19_98_5\">5<\/sup>Canten al Se\u00f1or con la c\u00edtara,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_5\">con la c\u00edtara y con voz melodiosa;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.6\" class=\"v19_98_6\">6<\/sup>con clarines y al son de trompetas,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_6\">aclamen al Se\u00f1or, el rey.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.7\" class=\"v19_98_7\">7<\/sup>Que brame el mar y cuanto lo llena,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_7\">el mundo y los que en \u00e9l habitan;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.8\" class=\"v19_98_8\">8<\/sup>que batan palmas los r\u00edos<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_8\">y los montes se alegren juntos<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.98.9\" class=\"v19_98_9\">9<\/sup>ante el Se\u00f1or que viene,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_9\">que llega a juzgar a la tierra:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_9\">juzgar\u00e1 al mundo con justicia<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_98_9\">y con rectitud a los pueblos.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"98","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.98","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.98.9","order":"19098","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/98","display":"SALMOS 98","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.97","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.99","nextChapter":{"auditid":"0","label":"","text":"<div id=\"Ps.99\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"ms2\">Salmo 99 (98)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Santo es el Se\u00f1or<\/h3>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_1\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.1\" class=\"v19_99_1\">1<\/sup>El Se\u00f1or es rey,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_1\">que los pueblos se estremezcan;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_1\">sobre querubines tiene su trono,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_1\">que tiemble la tierra.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_2\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.2\" class=\"v19_99_2\">2<\/sup>El Se\u00f1or es grande en Si\u00f3n,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_2\">sobre todos los pueblos se alza.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.3\" class=\"v19_99_3\">3<\/sup>Que alaben tu nombre grande y temible:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_3\">\u00a1\u00c9l es santo!<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.4\" class=\"v19_99_4\">4<\/sup>Rey poderoso que amas la justicia,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_4\">t\u00fa mismo estableciste la equidad;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_4\">la justicia y el derecho<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_4\">t\u00fa instauraste en Jacob.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.5\" class=\"v19_99_5\">5<\/sup>Alaben al Se\u00f1or nuestro Dios,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_5\">p\u00f3strense ante el estrado de sus pies:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_5\">\u00a1\u00c9l es santo!<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.6\" class=\"v19_99_6\">6<\/sup>De sus sacerdotes, Mois\u00e9s y Aar\u00f3n;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_6\">de los que invocaban su nombre, Samuel:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_6\">ellos llamaban al Se\u00f1or y \u00e9l les respond\u00eda.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.7\" class=\"v19_99_7\">7<\/sup>Desde la columna de nube hablaba con ellos;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_7\">ellos respetaban sus mandatos<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_7\">y la ley que les hab\u00eda dado.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.8\" class=\"v19_99_8\">8<\/sup>Se\u00f1or, Dios nuestro, t\u00fa les respond\u00edas;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_8\">t\u00fa eras para ellos el Dios que perdona<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_8\">y quien castiga sus maldades.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.99.9\" class=\"v19_99_9\">9<\/sup>Alaben al Se\u00f1or nuestro Dios,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_9\">p\u00f3strense ante su santo monte,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_99_9\">porque santo es el Se\u00f1or nuestro Dios.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"99","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.99","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.99.9","order":"19099","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/99","display":"SALMOS 99","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.98","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.100","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"prevChapter":{"auditid":"0","label":"","text":"<div id=\"Ps.97\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"ms2\">Salmo 97 (96)<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">El Se\u00f1or es due\u00f1o de toda la tierra<\/h3>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_1\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.1\" class=\"v19_97_1\">1<\/sup>El Se\u00f1or es rey, que se goce la tierra,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_1\">que se alegren los pa\u00edses lejanos.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_2\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.2\" class=\"v19_97_2\">2<\/sup>La bruma y la niebla lo rodean,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_2\">la justicia y el derecho sostienen su trono.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.3\" class=\"v19_97_3\">3<\/sup>El fuego avanza ante \u00e9l,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_3\">abrasa en derredor a sus rivales;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.4\" class=\"v19_97_4\">4<\/sup>sus rayos iluminan el orbe,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_4\">los ve la tierra y tiembla.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.5\" class=\"v19_97_5\">5<\/sup>Los montes se funden como cera ante el Se\u00f1or,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_5\">ante el due\u00f1o de toda la tierra;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.6\" class=\"v19_97_6\">6<\/sup>los cielos pregonan su justicia,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_6\">todos los pueblos contemplan su gloria.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.7\" class=\"v19_97_7\">7<\/sup>Que se averg\u00fcencen los id\u00f3latras,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_7\">los que cifran en los \u00eddolos su orgullo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_7\">que se postren ante \u00e9l todos los dioses.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.8\" class=\"v19_97_8\">8<\/sup>Si\u00f3n lo oye y se llena de gozo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_8\">se alegran las ciudades de Jud\u00e1<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_8\">a causa de tus juicios, Se\u00f1or.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.9\" class=\"v19_97_9\">9<\/sup>Porque t\u00fa eres, Se\u00f1or,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_9\">el Alt\u00edsimo en toda la tierra,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_9\">t\u00fa quien se alza sobre los dioses.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_10\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.10\" class=\"v19_97_10\">10<\/sup>Odien el mal los que aman al Se\u00f1or:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_10\">\u00e9l guarda la vida de sus fieles,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_10\">los libra de las garras del malvado.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_11\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.11\" class=\"v19_97_11\">11<\/sup>La luz se propaga para el justo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_11\">la alegr\u00eda para quienes son rectos.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_12\"><sup id=\"Ps.97.12\" class=\"v19_97_12\">12<\/sup>\u00a1Al\u00e9grense, justos, en el Se\u00f1or,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_97_12\">alaben su santo nombre!<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"97","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.97","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.97.12","order":"19097","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/97","display":"SALMOS 97","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.96","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.98","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]}